Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE occurs

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where both occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION for cases where activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION occurs

Name: Total duration from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Payment Handled' in cases where payment is eventually made
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Payment Handled for cases where activity Payment Handled occurs

Name: Minimum time taken for a case to be resubmitted after 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR for cases where activity Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and any subsequent 'Request Payment' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Request Payment for cases where activity Request Payment occurs

Name: Total time from first 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases with multiple submissions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Longest time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to case closure, regardless of outcome
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002527E14D8B0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where the declaration is reconsidered
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION for cases where activity Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION occurs

Name: Average duration of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' activity in the context of the entire process timeline
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases involving budget owner approval after rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER for cases where activity Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER occurs
